Requirements: 

OS: Raspbian/Debian Wheeze
HTTP: Apache2 is reccomended although any will work fine. (sudo apt-get install apache2)
Language Dependancies: PHP5 (sudo apt-get install php5

Upload everything within the .ZIP file you downloaded from GitHub into a folder called raspcontrol within your web accessible directory (Apaches Default is location is /var/www

If you're accessing Apaches web directory on your Raspberry Pi (using startx) you can navigate to http://localhost/raspcontrol/instructions, if you're accessing it from another computer on your Network you will need to navigate to http://your.iternal.ip/raspcontrol/instructions.

Login with:
Username: admin
Password: admin

